.modal-backdrop.in
  .modal-dialog.modal-md.modal-alert
    header.modal-body
      p.p.strong Apply changes to other containers?
      p.p There are other containers in this cluster with the same repository. These changes will apply to those containers as well.
    footer.modal-footer.clearfix
      button.btn.btn-sm.gray.float-left(
        ng-click = "CMC.actions.cancel()"
      ) Cancel
      button.btn.btn-sm.green.float-right(
        ng-click = "CMC.actions.confirm()"
      ) Apply to All
